"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143395","Department of Health","false","2014-11-19","<p>The Department is continuing negotiations for the supply of the meningococcal B vaccine Bexsero<sup>®</sup> with the manufacturer Novartis with a view to securing a cost-effective price as recommended by the Joint Committee on Vaccination and Immunisation.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Plans for inclusion of the Bexsero<sup>®</sup> in the routine infant immunisation programme will depend on the outcome of these negotiations, which will be completed as quickly as practicable.</p><p> </p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison",,"2014-11-19T16:08:45.727Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143395/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143395/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143395/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-11-07","Meningitis: Vaccination","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, what timescale his Department has set for rolling out the meningococcal group B vaccine Bexsero to all babies as part of the national immunisation programme.","false","Biography information for Mrs Sharon Hodgson","Washington and Sunderland West","Mrs Sharon Hodgson","213865"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143396","Department of Health","false","2014-11-19","<p>Work is under way by Departmental officials to explore a possible acquisition of a carriage study, as suggested by the Joint Committee on Vaccination and Immunisation.</p><p> </p>","Battersea","Jane Ellison",,"2014-11-19T16:16:44.583Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143396/answer","Biography information for Jane Ellison","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143396/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/143396/answer",,,,,"17","Health","Health","2014-11-07","Meningitis: Vaccination","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health, if his Department will commission a carriage study into whether the meningococcal group B vaccine Bexsero should be extended and administered to adolescents and students.","false","Biography information for Mrs Sharon Hodgson","Washington and Sunderland West","Mrs Sharon Hodgson","213866"
